Babington Macaulay Junior Seminary bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ agụmakwụkwọ onwe onye na Agunfoye-Lugbusi Village, Ikorodu, Lagos Naijiria
Ọ bụ ndị Anglican dioceses atọ jikọtara aka na Lagos Province, Lagos West na Lagos Mainland, Church of Nigeria.

N'afọ 2003, ọ sonyere na asọmpi sayensị megide ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ndị ọzọ na Naịjirịa, gụnyere Redeemer's International School, Effortswill High School, Supreme Education Centre, Caleb International School, Atlantic Hall na Grace High School.
Onajide ndị na-ese ụkpụrụ ụlọ nke Lagos mepụtara atụmatụ ukwu maka ogige ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ.
Onye isi mbụ nke BMJS bụ Ven n'oge ahụ
Akin Odejide, nke Ven kwadoro nke ọma

Tunde Oduwole na ndị nkuzi dị elu; Maazị Itiolu, Maazị Arabambi, Maaziri Alagbala, Maazir Jolayemi, Maazọ Babarinsa, Maazik Oki, Maazig Akinrenmi na ihe ndị ọzọ.
E nyere ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ dị ka ụlọ akwụkwọ onwe onye kachasị mma na Ikorodu.
Onye isi ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ ugbu a bụ Rev Cannon Dr.Bamidele Osunyomi Adesina (Septemba 2018 ruo oge a).

BRESCAG bụ mkpụmkpụ maka ụlọ akwụkwọ ndị ọsụ ụzọ sonyere na asọmpi ahụ ~ Babington Macaulay Junior Seminary, Redeemers International Secondary School, Efforts will School, Solid Foundation School, Caleb International, Atlantic Hall na Grace High School n'otu n'otu
Asọmpi ahụ malitere n'afọ 1998 ma na-eme kwa afọ kemgbe ahụ n'ebe dị iche iche na-enye ụmụ akwụkwọ ohere ịchọta ihe ha na-eme nke ọma, ma na agụmakwụkwọ ma na egwuregwu
Asọmpi gụnyere egwuregwu,egwuregwu, asọmpi sayensị, nka na arụmụka.
